node.title: TV shows canceled or ended in 2022
node.description: "Bull," "The Walking Dead," even Ellen -- here's what, and who, is leaving your TV.
node.content: ["It's official: The sixth season of the CBS legal drama \"Bull\" will be its last. Series star Michael Weatherly made the announcement on Twitter, and the finale is expected to air in May 2022.", "Here's a roundup of some of the biggest titles from ABC, CBS, Fox, NBC, Netflix and more that audiences will no longer see after 2022. Some of the shows have been canceled, while others are voluntarily retiring sometime this year. \u00a0"]
